title: Ebro In The Morning - Emmy Nominations, Radio Ratings Wars + The Water Is Dangerous
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 7/6/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio discussing Lizzo's potential to EGOT, the recent Emmy nominations, and the future of White Ish Wednesday! 

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!

Subscribe to "Summer Jam: Through The Years" - hosted by Laura Stylez!
